      <title>拜登告诉内塔尼亚胡美国的支持取决于保护平民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-tells-netanyahu-us-support-hinges-on-protecting-civilians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登告诉以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，美国对加沙战争的支持将取决于保护平民的新措施，这是美国领导人立场的转变，他在死亡人数不断增加的情况下面临着对以色列采取更强硬立场的越来越大的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-tells-netanyahu-us-support-hinges-on-protecting-civilians</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚将提供学生贷款以扩大受教育机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nigeria-to-offer-student-loans-to-expand-access-to-education</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布签署了一项法律，设立学生贷款基金，以扩大这个西非国家生活成本危机中无力支付学费的人的受教育机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nigeria-to-offer-student-loans-to-expand-access-to-education</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈阿密因交通强烈反对而放弃发行 25 亿美元债券的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/miami-abandons-plan-for-2-5-billion-bond-after-transit-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密戴德县正在取消一项 25 亿美元的债务计划，此前该计划遭到强烈反对，其中包括为改善全美最差的交通网络之一提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/miami-abandons-plan-for-2-5-billion-bond-after-transit-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以言论自由为由败诉佐治亚州案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trump-loses-bid-to-dismiss-georgia-case-on-free-speech-grounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐治亚州一名法官拒绝驳回针对唐纳德·特朗普和几名共同被告的敲诈勒索指控，裁定他们推翻 2020 年大选的努力不受第一修正案的保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trump-loses-bid-to-dismiss-georgia-case-on-free-speech-grounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:39:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约表示，特朗普债券公司应提供资源证明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trump-bond-firm-should-offer-proof-of-resources-new-york-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 要求上诉法院要求唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在 10 天内证明，如果他的法律挑战失败，为该州民事欺诈案提供 1.75 亿美元保证金的公司在财务上有能力兑现承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trump-bond-firm-should-offer-proof-of-resources-new-york-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 17:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在盟友批评投票后，委内瑞拉向外国选举监督机构求助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/venezuela-reaches-out-to-foreign-election-monitors-after-allies-criticize-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉表示，由于尼古拉斯·马杜罗在 7 月 28 日总统选举前面临不公平的批评，该国将于下周开始与国际选举观察团进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/venezuela-reaches-out-to-foreign-election-monitors-after-allies-criticize-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:54:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多表示不会在预算中对中产阶级增税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-says-he-won-t-raise-taxes-on-middle-class-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，加拿大即将出台的预算不会包括对中产阶级征收新税，但没有评论政府是否会采取其他措施来增加税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-says-he-won-t-raise-taxes-on-middle-class-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的顾问敦促亚马逊和家得宝保留巴尔的摩的就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-team-urges-amazon-home-depot-to-keep-baltimore-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的顾问已致电巴尔的摩的主要雇主——包括 Amazon.com Inc. 和 Home Depot Inc. –据知情人士透露，尽管桥梁倒塌导致该市港口关闭，但仍鼓励他们保住工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-team-urges-amazon-home-depot-to-keep-baltimore-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁国会拒绝就劳力士丑闻弹劾博卢阿特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-rejects-impeaching-boluarte-over-rolex-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁国会周四驳回了针对不受欢迎的总统迪娜·博卢阿特 (Dina Boluarte) 的两项弹劾动议，后者正在就非法致富和使用劳力士手表的政治丑闻展开刑事调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-rejects-impeaching-boluarte-over-rolex-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
